movie.title: Along for the Ride
movie.description_intro: Along for the Ride is a documentary film that explores the highs, lows and ultimately the phoenix-like ascension of iconic Hollywood maverick Dennis Hopper, as seen through the eyes of his mysterious longtime "right-hand man," Satya de la Manitou.

movies.title: Fresh Meat
movies.summary: A dysfunctional gang of criminals takes a middle class Maori family hostage and discovers too late that they are cannibals.

movies.title: Raptor Ranch
movies.summary: Raptor Ranch is sci-fi, horror flick with all the trappings of a juicy, action-adventure movie with comic relief thrown in. They're not just raising cattle in Texas. They're raising 70 million years of prehistoric terror. Move over Jurassic Park; here's come Raptor Ranch! Yee-Haw!

movies.title: The New Frontier
movies.summary: In 1889, pioneers race ahead of the law to claim free land in Oklahoma, forming wide-open towns. In one such, citizens elect Milt Dawson to challenge the self-appointed rule of gambler Ace Holmes, only to have him shot in the back. But leading the next batch of settlers is Milt's quick-on-the-draw son John, who gets help from friendly outlaws.

movies.title: Canadian Strain
movies.summary: When cannabis becomes legal in Canada, boutique weed dealer Anne Banting is swiftly run out of business by the biggest gangsters in town - the government.
